Three models are defined by this FCC ID. *WAP5204 (2MB Flash, 16MB RAM, 1x Ethernet, no USB) *WR5204U (4MB Flash, 32MB RAM, 2x Ethernet) *WR5204UE (4MB Flash, 32MB RAM, 2x Ethernet)
